* What is the Go Challenge
.image JOSHSoftware_LogoStack_.png 

- Monthly programming challenge
- Open to individuals not groups

* Motivation

- Hands on learning the language
- Small isolated problem to solve
- Feedback from experts
- Out of the day to day programmer routine


* Prizes
- Gift Cards
- Books + eBooks
- T-shirts, stickers, ...
- Interview with the winner
.image gopher.png 

* How does it work
- A new Go Challenge every [[http://golang-challenge.com/][1st of month]]
- Code -> Zip -> Email to [[mailto:gochallenge@joshsoftware.com][gochallenge@joshsoftware.com ]]
- Re-submit allowed < deadline
- Challenge author selects the winners
# keep deadline in mind, timezone

